# Releases

To release a new version of the tool:

* ensure that the version has been bumped already
* git tag v`poetry version -s`
* git push --tags
* poetry build
* poetry publish
* poetry version patch
* git add pyproject.toml
* git commit -m "Bumps to version `poetry version -s`"
* git push
* edit the release notes on <https://github.com/beaufour/flickr-download/releases>

## PyPi Authentication

To configure auth for PyPi for the first time do:

    poetry config pypi-token.pypi my-token
